Description.Name: Land Air Mech Engine
Description.Details: This model is an Improved Reproduction, modified by Comstar Technicians for higher thrust output. This engine was designed by ,and based off an similar engine salavaged from the Solaris Gladiator Hi MAX's Marauder DER. The engine was salvaged after losing a Solaris match. The engine was developed in secret by Comstar, and built directly to support their own MAD-DER production run.
